Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(47557,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
## Action STD
Call AS_NATCOD0(VALEUR) From SUBSTY
If mkstat=2
 [M]NATCOD0(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo NATCOD0(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_NATCOD0(zc) From W1STY1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_NATCOD0(zc) From W1STY1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_NATCOD0(zc) From W1STY1
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_NATCOD0(zc) From W1STY1
